snippet.title: Under Cover VR - Official Announce Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Meet Red-Eye and Magnum, see action-packed gameplay, and learn about your mission in this announcement trailer for Under Cover, an upcoming game featuring classic lightgun action, an active cover system, and more. Under Cover will be available on Meta Quest on February 15, 2024.
